OL,3,CGang bundled pregnant woman into van
OL,4,Cand threatened to cut her fingers off
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed after
OL,7,Fkidnapping a pregnant mother from
OL,8,Foutside her home and threatening to
OL,9,Fcut her fingers off, the Metropolitan
OL,10,FPolice have said.
OL,12,FAudi Johnson, 35, Ahmad Ghiasi, 26,
OL,13,Fand Nicholas Mitchell, 55, bundled
OL,14,Ftheir victim who was six months
OL,15,Fpregnant, into the back of a van after
OL,16,Fshe left her north London home on the
OL,17,Fmorning of May 10 2024.
