OL,6,FShe was blindfolded and bound at the
OL,7,Fwrist with cable ties by the gang as
OL,8,Fthey sped away, before they fired
OL,9,Fquestions at about her partner where
OL,10,Fone of them threatened: "If you lie to
OL,11,Fme I'm gonna kick the baby out your
OL,12,Fstomach."
OL,14,FThen a series of phone calls was made
OL,15,Fto her partner as the gang threatened
OL,16,Fto cut off her fingers if he did not
OL,17,Fquickly carry out their demands for
OL,18,Fmoney and valuable jewellery, the
OL,19,Fpolice said.
