OL,6,FJohnson, Ghiasi and Mitchell were
OL,7,Ffound guilty of conspiracy to kidnap
OL,8,Flast month after a six-week trial at
OL,9,FKingston Crown Court.
OL,11,FThey were members of a London-based
OL,12,Fgang, who had been contracted to carry
OL,13,Fout the kidnapping, the force said.
OL,15,FThe 36 year-old woman said she has not
OL,16,Fbeen able to go home since the
OL,17,Ftraumatic ordeal and spent the rest of
OL,18,Fher pregnancy sleeping on her sister's
OL,19,Fcouch.
