OL,6,FIn her victim impact statement, she
OL,7,Ftold the court: "The incident ruined
OL,8,Fmy life. I will never be the same
OL,9,Fperson again. I am having to start my
OL,10,Flife all over again.
OL,12,F"I will forever have fear and paranoia
OL,13,Fas part of my life now. I didn't
OL,14,Fdeserve to be a victim of what
OL,15,Fhappened to me. And to top it off, it
OL,16,Fwas all made so much worse by being
OL,17,Fpregnant.
