OL,6,F"This will always be something that
OL,7,Fwill be part of my pregnancy, which is
OL,8,Fmeant to be a happy experience, and
OL,9,Fwill always be something that is a
OL,10,Fpart of my daughter."
OL,12,FShe was kidnapped as she waited for a
OL,13,Fcab to take her to a personal training
OL,14,Fsession with her mother and sister.
OL,16,FShe was walked along the curb close to
OL,17,Fher Enfield home, when she was
OL,18,Fsuddenly grabbed and thrown into the
OL,19,Fback of a white Ford Transit van.
