OL,6,FA police spokesman said the Met's
OL,7,FFlying Squad responded to the crime
OL,8,Fimmediately.
OL,10,FThey tracked the van using CCTV and
OL,11,Flocated the vehicle the same night the
OL,12,Fhostage was recovered.
OL,14,FDNA evidence, fingerprint impressions
OL,15,Fand mobile phone data were used to
OL,16,Fidentify the suspects.
OL,18,FThe police said Johnson, of Cranberry
OL,19,FClose, Northolt, had pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fconspiracy to kidnap and was sentenced
OL,21,Fto five years and four months.
